Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar sankarar bargo ta SARS (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar, ta haifar da bala'in ɗan adam wanda ya kai mutuwar mutane sama da 3,000 da kamuwa da cutar sama da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya.
Kamar yadda yake tare da SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama kamuwa da cutar daga malam buɗe ido kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya ta hanyar irin wannan ɓangaren jikin.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan tsanani da ƙananan mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana yaduwa da sauri, yana shafar maza fiye da matasa, tsofaffi da mata fiye da mata.
A sakamakon karuwar wallafe-wallafen da ake samu game da cutar, wannan labarin ya yi ƙoƙari ya samar da cikakken bayani game da abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin bincike mai sauri.
Za mu yi amfani da wannan don nazarin cututtuka, gano abubuwan da ke haifar da su, nazarin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, kimantawa da rigakafi.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan bita zai ba da ƙarin haske game da wannan cuta mai barazana kuma ya taimaka wajen kawar da ita.
