Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama ɗan gajeren ɗan littafin da aka ƙirƙira ta hanyar orf3b da kuma kwayar halitta mai fitar da ƙwayoyin cuta ta hanyar orf8.
Ko da yake orf3b na SARS-CoV-2 yana iya zama alamar cutar kwayar cutar kuma yana hana IFNβ, orf8 ba shi da wani yanki ko tsari na tasiri da aka sani.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairun 2020, Zhou da sauransu sun gabatar da tsarin cryo-EM na cikakken mutum ACE2 wanda ya haɗu da B0AT1, mai jigilar amino acid, a ƙuduri na 2.9 Å.
