Yawancin lokaci, bayan kwayar cutar ta mamaye mai masaukin, tsarin rigakafin asalin mai masaukin yana fara gane shi ta hanyar masu karɓar karɓar hoto (PRRs), gami da masu karɓar nau'in C-type lectin-like, mai karɓar haraji (TLR), mai karɓar NOD-like (NLR), da mai karɓar RIG-I (RLR).
Ta hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar tana haifar da kumburi, yana haifar da haɓakar ƙwayoyin dendritic (tsarin rigakafi) da kuma iyakance yaduwar kwayar cutar, kuma yana haifar da nau'ikan I interferons (IFNs) wanda ke sa kwayoyin phagocyte su hanzarta narkar da ƙwayoyin cuta na kwayar cutar.
Duk da haka, furotin N na SARS-CoV na iya taimaka wa kwayar cutar ta tsira daga ƙwayoyin cuta.
Ba da daɗewa ba, amsawar rigakafin da ta dace ta shiga cikin yaƙi da kwayar cutar.
Kwayoyin T, ciki har da CD4 + da CD8 + T cells, suna taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen hana cutar MERS.
Kwayoyin CD4 + T suna motsa ƙwayoyin B don samar da maganin rigakafi da ke yaƙi da kwayar cutar, yayin da ƙwayoyin CD8 + T ke kashe ƙwayoyin da ke dauke da kwayar cutar kai tsaye.
Kwayoyin T masu taimakawa suna samar da wani kwayar halitta mai kumburi don taimakawa kwayoyin kariya.
Koyaya, CoVs na iya haifar da mutuwar ƙwayoyin T kuma ya hana ayyukan T.
