Juyin halitta da daidaitawa sun ba da damar kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoVs) da kuma mahalarta su, gami da mutane, su ci gaba tare har tsawon shekaru.
A shekara ta 2003, an gano cewa wasu ƙwayoyin cuta guda biyu na mutum (HCoVs) suna haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi kamar sanyi.
A cikin ɓarkewar cutar SARS da MERS, cutar HCoV ta zama mai rikitarwa da haɗari ga rayuwa.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a babban yankin China a ƙarshen 2019 kamar ya ba da ƙarin haske ga CoVs, yana ba mu mamaki da yawan kamuwa da cutar amma yana da ƙananan cututtuka idan aka kwatanta da takwaransa na SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV tana yaduwa daga dabba zuwa mutum, kuma fahimtar asalin dabbobi na HCoVs zai ba mu damar yin aiki sosai.
Yawancin HCoVs da aka fara kamuwa da su daga ƙuda sun samo asali ne daga ƙudaje marasa cutar.
An kuma gano masu karɓar baƙi na wasu HCoVs.
Gano dabbobi masu karɓar baƙi yana da alaƙa kai tsaye da rigakafin cututtukan ɗan adam.
Binciken hulɗar masu karɓar COVID-19 a cikin dabbobi na iya samar da mahimman bayanai game da cutar COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, mun gabatar da cikakken nazarin ilimin game da nau'ikan HCoVs guda bakwai da ke akwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin binciken su da kuma asalin su na dabbobi da kuma yaduwar jinsuna.
Yana da mahimmanci cewa mun kwatanta da kuma tattauna bambancin HCoVs daban-daban daga yanayin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar da sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
Wannan labarin ya tattauna game da annobar cutar COVID-19 (Covid-19) ta yanzu.
Bugu da ƙari, ya nuna mahimmancin buƙatun don nasarar sauye-sauye daga mai karɓar baƙi da kuma tasirin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar akan tsananin cutar.
Kwayoyin cuta na corona (CoVs) suna cikin dangin coronaviruses waɗanda ke da nau'ikan ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya tare da garkuwar garkuwar.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta suna da girman kilobases 26 zuwa 32 kuma sun sami mafi girman jinsuna tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA, waɗanda ake kira CoVs saboda siffar su ta hanyar microscope.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta marasa rarrabuwa waɗanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi manyan allon biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) waɗanda ke fassara juna a matsayin pp1a da pp1ab polyproteins masu kwafi.
Polyproteins suna aiki don samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari, wanda aka ƙaddara nsp1-16.
Sauran sassan tsarin ORFs tare da kwayoyin halitta sun hada da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Yawancin ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman na kwayoyin halitta suna ƙunshe da ƙwayoyin cuta daban-daban na CoVs.
Dangane da tasirin kwayoyin halitta daban-daban, an rarraba kwayoyin cuta na CoVs zuwa gida huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV), waɗanda ke da ƙwayoyin cuta na beta-CoV da ke da ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs da yawa, kuma an rarraba su cikin gida huɗu (A, B, C da D).
A cikin shaidar nazarin kwayoyin halitta, tsuntsaye sun kasance manyan wuraren tattara gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs, yayin da jemage da masu cizon sauro ke aiki a matsayin tushen asalin yawancin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs.
Ko da a cikin dubunnan shekaru, CoVs sun kasance cikin jerin ƙuntatawa na jinsuna, wasu daga cikinsu sun fito da gaggawa don haifar da barkewar cutar ɗan adam.
A yau, an gano nau'ikan HCoVs guda bakwai da ke cutar ɗan adam.
Daga cikin su, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune masu cutar alpha-CoVs.
Sauran cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta guda biyar da aka haɗa sune HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Cutar cututtukan HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya kamar sanyi da / ko amai.
Idan aka kwatanta, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon SARS-CoV-2 wanda aka gano, suna da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar kwayar cuta, wanda ke haifar da mummunan kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar numfashi tare da haɗarin kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da cututtukan huhu masu tsanani a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa.
An ware HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga hanci daga mai cutar sanyi a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar nazarin HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, waɗanda ke haifar da iyakancewar alamun cutar.
A gaskiya ma, kafin barkewar SARS, an yarda da cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoVs ba ta da haɗari.
Cutar SARS da ta ɓarke a shekara ta 2003 ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin mummunar annoba a tarihin zamani, ta kamu da mutane fiye da 8,000 kuma ta kashe kusan 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar MERS ta Gabas ta Tsakiya ta haifar da barkewar annoba a yankin Larabawa, kuma ta bazu zuwa sauran duniya a cikin keɓewa.
HCoV (2019-nCoV) wanda ya bayyana a cikin 2019, wanda daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, shine babban dalilin cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane 3,120 da kamuwa da mutane sama da 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
