Wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba a ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020 a cikin South China Morning Post ya nuna cewa, bayan gano barkewar cutar zuwa 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, mai yiwuwa mutum mai shekaru 55 a lardin Hubei ne ya fara kamuwa da cutar. Ko da yake sabon yanayin ya ragu sosai a China, akwai tashin hankali a Italiya, Iran da Koriya ta Kudu, kuma a karon farko, adadin sabbin cututtukan da ke faruwa a wajen China ya zarce adadin sabbin cututtukan da ke faruwa a China, in ji WHO a ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Akwai yiwuwar a rage yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar da ke nuna alamun rashin lafiya.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an ba da rahoton ƙananan cututtukan tsakanin matasa masu shekaru 19 zuwa ƙasa, wanda ya kai ƙasa da kashi 2.4 cikin ɗari na cututtukan a duniya.Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan mutanen Burtaniya za su sami rigakafin garken bayan sun kamu da cutar.
Ana kiran mutane da ke da cutar da cutar COVID-19 waɗanda aka gwada su kuma aka tabbatar da tabbatacce a ƙarƙashin hanyoyin hukuma.
A ranar 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawanta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain da Switzerland suna da manufofin hukuma waɗanda ke hana yin gwajin cutar ga mutanen da ke da alamun rashin lafiya.
Wani bincike da aka buga a ranar 16 ga Maris ya nuna cewa kimanin kashi 86% na masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a China ba a gano su ba har zuwa 23 ga Janairu, kuma waɗannan cututtukan da ba a lissafa ba sune tushen kamuwa da kashi 79% na masu kamuwa da cutar.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka fitar a ranar 30 ga Maris ya kiyasta cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi adadin wadanda aka bayar da rahoton.
Hasashen asali na lambar asali ta haihuwa (R0) don COVID-19 shine 1.4 zuwa 2.4.
Wani bincike da Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Amurka ta wallafa ya kammala cewa zai iya zama 5.7.
Yawancin mutane da ke fama da COVID-19 suna murmurewa.
Ga waɗanda ba su yi hakan ba, lokacin daga bayyanar cututtuka zuwa mutuwa ya kasance tsakanin kwanaki 6 zuwa 41, kuma yawanci kwanaki 14 ne don bayyanar cututtuka.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, kusan mutane 97,000 ne suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, kashi 80% na mutanen da suka mutu a China sun haura shekaru 60 da haihuwa, kuma kashi 75% suna da wasu cututtukan da suka gabata, gami da cututtukan zuciya da ciwon sukari.
Wannan ba ya haɗa da mutuwar da ba a bincika ba, kamar waɗanda suka mutu a gida, gidajen tsofaffi, da sauransu. Saboda haka, ainihin adadin mutuwar COVID-19 na iya zama mafi girma.
Wani ɓangare na bayanan da aka samu daga Italiya ya nuna cewa adadin mutuwar a lokacin annobar ya ninka ainihin mutuwar COVID sau 4 zuwa 5.
Wata mai magana da yawun Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka (CDC) ta yarda cewa mun san cewa yawan mutanen da suka mutu an rage su. Ana yin ƙididdiga a Amurka kuma rahotanni marasa tabbas suna tabbatar da wannan da'awar. Irin wannan ƙididdigar ba ta da yawa a lokacin annobar, kamar lokacin annobar cutar alade ta H1N1.
An samu mutuwar farko a waje da kasar Sin a Philippines a ranar 1 ga watan Fabrairu, kuma an samu mutuwar farko a waje da Asiya a Faransa a ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu.
A wasu kasashen waje da ke da alaka da kasar Sin, kamar Iran, Koriya ta Kudu da Italiya, an samu mutuwar mutane fiye da dozin kafin ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, an samu rahoton mutuwar mutane a kasashe da yankuna sama da 40 a kowace nahiya sai dai Antarctica.
Waɗannan ƙididdigar sun bambanta a cikin lokaci daga yanki zuwa yanki, kuma yawancin abubuwan da ke shafar su sune yawan gwaji, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani, tsawon lokacin kamuwa da cuta, da kuma yanayin alƙaluma kamar shekaru, jinsi, da yanayin gaba ɗaya.
Bayanai daga Jami'ar Johns Hopkins sun nuna cewa a ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, adadin mace-mace da cutar a duniya ya kai kashi 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204).
