Waɗannan sun haɗa da ma'aikata waɗanda ke da haɗuwa da jama'a gaba ɗaya, kamar makarantu, yanayin aiki mai cunkoson jama'a, da wasu wuraren sayar da kayayyaki masu tsada. Hakanan, sarrafawa na injiniya don ƙungiyoyin haɗari masu haɗari sun haɗa da sanya kayan aikin laser masu inganci sosai, haɓaka ƙarar iska, sanya shinge na zahiri kamar masu toshe filastik masu tsalle-tsalle da sanya rigunan motsa jiki don sabis na abokin ciniki, rarraba kayan aiki na yau da kullun, ɗaukar kayan aiki na yau da kullun, ɗaukar kayan aiki na gaggawa, da kuma ƙarin shirye-shirye don ƙungiyoyin haɗari.
