Lokacin da akwai ƙananan zuwa matsakaiciyar yaduwar jama'a, ana iya aiwatar da dabarun nisantar da jama'a kamar tafiye-tafiye, tarurruka, da sauran manyan tarurruka kamar yin motsa jiki ko darussan waƙa, ko cin abinci a cikin kofi, ƙara sarari tsakanin teburin, jinkirta jadawalin don hana rikicewar lokacin isowa da tashi, iyakance baƙi marasa mahimmanci, da amfani da wuraren ofisoshin kiwon lafiya na musamman don yara masu alamun mura.
A lokacin da akwai yawan kamuwa da cutar a cikin al'ummomin asali, ana iya yin la'akari da fadada lokacin makaranta tare da dabarun nisantar zamantakewa. CDC ta ƙaddara cewa akwai ƙananan haɗarin lafiya na mutum ga jami'in tilasta yin aiki wanda ke gudanar da ayyukan yau da kullun.
Ana ba da shawarar cewa jami'an tilasta yin doka waɗanda ke fuskantar haɗuwa da tabbataccen ko wanda ake zargi da kamuwa da COVID-19 su bi irin wannan jagororin kamar masu aikin gaggawa, gami da amfani da kayan kariya na mutum.
